<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hello <%= @product.user_id.user %></h1>
    <p>
      The user <%= current_user.user %> likes one of your products (<%= @product.name %>),<br />
      you can contact with: <%= current_user.email %>.<br>
    </p>
    <p>
      If you want to take a look in the user's products, login to the site,<br />
      and search with the user's email.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for visit us and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>